Wilton Lackaye https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wilton_Lackaye 0 Wilton Lackaye (September 30, 1862 – August 22, 1932) was an American stage and film actor, who originated the role of Svengali (from the 1895 novel Trilby) in both stage and film.
